item.title: INITIATIVES
item.dc:creator: istec
item.content:encoded: ISTEC members are encouraged to participate in the free flow of information for the pursuit of technical excellence. By coordinating eminent personnel and resources from diverse geographical locations, ISTEC has developed a series of member-driven Initiatives: organized efforts that create activities to address specific areas of research, social, pedagogical, informational, and technological impact. Within each Initiative, projects are identified, planned, and implemented among members of the ISTEC network. Because they respond to the needs of our members and their communities, projects are dynamic and expandable, encouraging the creation of collaborative and highly coordinated networks that maximize the utilization of available resources. ISTEC initiatives and programs are intended as a response to issues identified as Grand Engineering Challenges in the XXIst century.
